与俄罗斯总统普京坐到谈判桌前，以结束俄乌战争。 俄罗斯总统普京 1 月 28 日在回答俄罗斯电视记者提问时说，俄方不反对与乌克兰的任何人进行谈判，但最终签署文件将是一个非常严肃的问题，应该确保俄罗斯和乌克兰长期安全。 来源：长安街知事微信 内容来源特朗普有了「停战计划」_ 俄罗斯 _ 连斯基 _ 美国"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-51254d50707da46a9de5905d567199ef_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "77 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/11430730141"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIztrh2LHnlrRKEAMaCTExMzI2MTkwNCDEqpG9BjAAODVAE3ILMTE0MzA3MzAxNDF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1738915847.371797", "card_id": "Q_10992857180", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "孩子提问「为什么以天来看时间就很慢，以年来看时间就很快」？你会如何给他解答？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如题那位伙伴来回答"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-844eead8f8c438129fc421b4a14eca0b_1440w.webp"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/10992857180"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIztrh2LHnlrRKEAMaCTExMzE3NDU4MCDCgPS8BjAAODJAFHILMTA5OTI4NTcxODB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1738915847.372045", "card_id": "Q_11374137669", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 52}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "亲戚说话不好听，是要反驳还是沉闷不语？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "给你讲道理，给你洗脑，说一些比较绝对的。 自己没有什么本事，反过来还要给你说教 行行行，你是长辈。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2f6f19e05637408ad6bd88cb13be4438_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/11374137669"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIzt